    <stitle>POWER STEERING PUMP: EATON MODEL BB135 R, L - ADJUSTMENTS</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcsubsec>
        <title>ADJUSTMENTS</title>
        <svcproc id="hl0500606" svcproctype="adjust" graphiccount="0">
            <title>BELT TENSION</title>
            <para>A belt that has been previously tensioned is considered to be a used belt and should be tightened to
                100 lbs. A belt that has never been tensioned is considered to be a new belt and should be tightened to
                125 lbs.
            </para>
            <para>Place Belt Tension Gage ZTSE-2312 (refer to
                <hotlnk document="s05006w_19.xml" xrefid="hl0500604">SPECIAL TOOLS</hotlnk>) or equivalent midway
                between the pulleys on drive belt being checked.
            </para>
        </svcproc>
    </svcsubsec>
